                <text type="forecast_winds">Northeasterly 10 to 15 knots turning northerly 15 to 20 knots early in the morning. Winds reaching up to 25 knots in the west in the late morning and early afternoon.</text>
                <text type="forecast_seas">Around 1 metre, increasing to 1 to 2 metres during the morning.</text>
