                <text type="forecast_winds">Northerly 15 to 20 knots tending northwesterly during the afternoon.</text>
                <text type="forecast_seas">1 to 2 metres.</text>
                <text type="forecast_swell1">Southwesterly 2 to 2.5 metres.</text>
